				<h2>Programming an ESC to have reverse mode</h2>
<p>How do you program an <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Electronic_speed_control" rel="nofollow">ESC</a> to have a reverse mode? We're looking to control an ESC from a servo board (for a <a href="http://greymatterrobotics.com/2012/09/18/the-hoverbot/" rel="nofollow">robotics project</a>).</p>

<p>Assuming that the input will be between 0 and 255, we're looking for 127 as off, 255 as fully forward and 0 as full reverse, so how do we achieve that?</p>

